<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="background-video">
            <source src="https://videos.pexels.com/video-files/3130284/3130284-uhd_2560_1440_30fps.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
        <div class="hero-overlay">
            <h1>Node js Development</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Node.js Development -->
    <section class="about-node">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Why Choose Node.js for Your Projects?</h2>
            <p>
                Node.js is a powerful, open-source runtime environment built on Chrome's V8 JavaScript engine. It is widely used for building fast, scalable, and efficient server-side applications. At Quickly Platforms, we specialize in delivering high-performance Node.js solutions tailored to your business needs.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether you're looking to build RESTful APIs, real-time applications, or microservices, Node.js provides the tools and flexibility to create robust and scalable solutions. Its event-driven, non-blocking architecture ensures exceptional performance and efficiency.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features of Node.js Development -->
    <section class="node-features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Key Features of Node.js Development</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Event-Driven Architecture</h3>
                    <p>Handle multiple requests simultaneously with Node.js's non-blocking, event-driven architecture.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Real-Time Applications</h3>
                    <p>Build real-time applications like chat apps and collaboration tools with WebSocket support.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Scalability</h3>
                    <p>Scale your applications horizontally and vertically to handle growing user demands.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Microservices</h3>
                    <p>Develop modular and independent services for better maintainability and scalability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>RESTful APIs</h3>
                    <p>Create lightweight and efficient APIs for seamless communication between systems.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Cross-Platform Development</h3>
                    <p>Build applications that run seamlessly across different platforms and environments.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Package Management</h3>
                    <p>Leverage npm, the largest package ecosystem, to integrate third-party libraries and tools.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>High Performance</h3>
                    <p>Utilize Node.js's single-threaded model for fast and efficient application performance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Streaming Data</h3>
                    <p>Process large amounts of data in real-time with Node.js's streaming capabilities.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Serverless Architecture</h3>
                    <p>Build serverless applications with Node.js for reduced infrastructure costs and scalability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Security</h3>
                    <p>Implement robust security practices to protect your applications from vulnerabilities.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <h3>Community Support</h3>
                    <p>Benefit from a vast and active Node.js community for continuous updates and support.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="call-to-action">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Build Your Node.js Project?</h2>
            <p>
                Contact us today to discuss your requirements and take the first step toward building a powerful Node.js application.
            </p>
            <a href="/Getintouch" class="btn-connect">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
